      public void printUserCamp(User user)
      Prints the camps that correspond to the given user. If the user is a Student, print the list of camps the student is registered for. If the user is a Staff, print the list of camps created by the staff.
      Parameters:

    • returnUserCamps

    • findCamp

      public Camp findCamp(CampList campList, String campName)
      Searches for a camp within the given campList that matches the given name.
      Parameters:

      campName - The name of the camp to be searched for.
